 this network were on\naverage at a distance equivalent to 5.1% of the image width from the centroids\nof the ground truth ROIs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Sep 2018 16:30:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-09"}
