 explanations is possible. Either (1) an\nAlfv\\'enic process preferentially accelerates or sustains proton beams and not\nalphas or (2) alpha particles are more susceptible to either an instability or\nCoulomb drag than proton beams.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Sep 2018 19:11:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-07"}
